2012 MERCEDES-BENZ C-CLASS C63 AMG COUPE PERFORMANCE PACK, 122 000 KM’S, R 559 950.00, FULL SERVICE HISTORY, IMMACULATE AND 100% ORIGINAL CONDITION, FULLY LOADED WITH EVERY EXTRA THAT AN AMG COMES WITH.
Well talk about a rare car to own, they do not produce these anymore and are never going to again. I will start off by saying the engine in this car is a true engineering master piece, there is no comparison the new C63, in my opinion a car like this has to have this engine, there is a saying that there is no replacement for displacement, and I tend to agree. There are literally 2 other C63 coupes on line in this price range and none of them will come close to this one in terms of extra’s, and condition. It’s also the only Black on Black C63 coupe currently on the net. When the original owner ordered this car from Mercedes they went to town on the extra’s list and to be honest I think I might run out of space, but here it goes. 
WHAT MAKES THIS CAR SO SPECIAL? 
•	AMG carbon-fibre/black piano lacquer-look trim
•	Adaptive brake lights
•	CAPACITY 6,2 LITRE
•	AMG Performance Package
•	Mirror package
•	Memory package
•	Black floor mats with AMG lettering
•	AMG outline edge carbon-fibre
•	Red-painted brake callipers
•	LEATHER DESIGNO UNICOLOR
•	Obsidian black metallic
•	Reversing camera
•	PARKTRONIC system (PTS)
•	Driving Assistance package Plus
•	PARKTRONIC
•	DISTRONIC PLUS incl. BAS Plus and PRE-SAFE® Brake
•	Active Blind Spot Assist
•	Active Lane Keeping Assist
•	LED-daytime running lights
•	AMG Driver's package
•	Electric panoramic Sliding sunroof
•	AMG SPEEDSHIFT MCT 7G-TRONIC
•	AMG rear-axle differential lock
•	INTELLIGENT LIGHT SYSTEM
•	AMG body styling
•	Harman Kardon® Logic 7® surround sound system
•	INCREASED POWER VERSION

This car is unbelievable, you the new owner will have one the greatest machines ever produced, I like to say that this car is angry, and when you drive it you will understand why I say that, the new owner will also own one the cleanest highest specked C63’s around.
